    ],
    "affected_lt": "9.1.7.23",
    "fixed_version": "9.1.7.23"
  },
  "analyst_note": "CVE-2018-0101: Double-free RCE in Cisco ASA WebVPN feature (IKEv1/IKEv2 fragmentation). CVSS 10.0. Affects ASA 9.1.x < 9.1.7.23, 9.2.x < 9.2.4.27, 9.4.x < 9.4.4.14, 9.6.x < 9.6.3.20, 9.7.x < 9.7.1.21. The /+CSCOE+/logon.html path is characteristic of Cisco ASA WebVPN/AnyConnect portals. Version disclosure may be suppressed \u2014 detect service presence and escalate for manual verification. Use Cisco PSIRT advisory for patching guidance.",
